HEADWORD: Novum
<hw>No"vum</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A game at dice,
properly called <altname>novem quinque</altname> (L., nine five), the
two principal throws being nine and five.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

